### HippoRAG Multi-Hop RAG API (PRODUCTION)
# ⚠️  WARNING: These requests target the PRODUCTION environment
# Production URL: https://ag-dt-ppl-api.felixtek.cloud/api/v1
# Use with caution - modifications affect live data
#
# HippoRAG provides multi-hop reasoning using Personalized PageRank (PPR) algorithm
# Best for: Complex reasoning queries requiring multiple inference steps
# Research shows: +20% improvement on multi-hop QA benchmarks
#
# Prerequisites:
# - Documents must be indexed with destination_type: "hipporag"
# - Sufficient storage at HIPPO_SAVE_DIR (/data/hipporag)
# - LLM configured for triple extraction and QA
#
# NOTE: These endpoints do NOT require authentication (consistent with /search/* routes)

@baseUrl = https://ag-dt-ppl-api.felixtek.cloud/api/v1


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. MULTI-HOP RETRIEVAL
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### HippoRAG Retrieve - Single Query
# Multi-hop retrieval using Personalized PageRank for complex queries
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/retrieve
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": ["What machine learning frameworks are used for natural language processing?"],
  "dataset_id": "default",
  "num_to_retrieve": 10,
  "include_metadata": true
}

### HippoRAG Retrieve - Multiple Related Queries
# Submit multiple queries for complex multi-hop reasoning
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/retrieve
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "What is Kubernetes used for?",
    "How does container orchestration work?",
    "What are the benefits of microservices?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "default",
  "num_to_retrieve": 15,
  "include_metadata": true
}

### HippoRAG Retrieve - Research Question
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/retrieve
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "How do transformer models handle attention mechanisms?",
    "What is the relationship between BERT and GPT architectures?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "research-papers",
  "num_to_retrieve": 12
}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 2. FULL RAG QA PIPELINE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### HippoRAG QA - Simple Question
# Full RAG pipeline: retrieval + answer generation
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": ["What are the advantages of using vector databases?"],
  "dataset_id": "default",
  "num_to_retrieve": 10,
  "generate_answer": true
}

### HippoRAG QA - Complex Multi-hop Question
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "How does Docker containerization relate to Kubernetes orchestration in microservices deployment?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "default",
  "num_to_retrieve": 15,
  "generate_answer": true
}

### HippoRAG QA - Comparative Analysis
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "Compare the performance characteristics of SQL and NoSQL databases for big data applications"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "technical-docs",
  "num_to_retrieve": 12,
  "generate_answer": true
}

### HippoRAG QA - Reasoning Chain
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "What is the relationship between neural networks, deep learning, and artificial intelligence?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "default",
  "num_to_retrieve": 10,
  "generate_answer": true
}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 3. TRIPLE EXTRACTION (OpenIE)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Extract Triples from Text
# Extract subject-predicate-object triples using Open Information Extraction
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/extract-triples
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "text": "Google developed TensorFlow for machine learning. TensorFlow supports deep learning models. Deep learning is a subset of artificial intelligence.",
  "language": "en"
}

### Extract Triples - Technical Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/extract-triples
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "text": "Kubernetes manages containerized applications. Docker creates containers. Containers package applications with dependencies. Microservices architecture uses containers for deployment.",
  "language": "en"
}

### Extract Triples - Research Paper Snippet
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/extract-triples
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "text": "Transformer models use self-attention mechanisms. BERT is a transformer-based model. GPT models generate text using transformers. Attention mechanisms improve sequence modeling.",
  "language": "en"
}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 4. ADVANCED MULTI-HOP EXAMPLES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Multi-hop Query - Causal Reasoning
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "Why do companies adopt cloud-native architectures and what are the cost implications?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "business-docs",
  "num_to_retrieve": 15,
  "generate_answer": true
}

### Multi-hop Query - Temporal Reasoning
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "How has machine learning evolved from statistical methods to deep learning?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "research-papers",
  "num_to_retrieve": 12,
  "generate_answer": true
}

### Complex Retrieval - Multiple Hops Required
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/retrieve
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "What is the relationship between API gateways, microservices, and service mesh?",
    "How do they interact in a distributed system?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "default",
  "num_to_retrieve": 20,
  "include_metadata": true
}

### Business Intelligence Query
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "What factors influence customer retention in SaaS businesses and how do they relate to pricing strategies?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "business-reports",
  "num_to_retrieve": 15,
  "generate_answer": true
}


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 5. COMPARISON WITH STANDARD SEARCH
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### HippoRAG Multi-hop (for complex reasoning)
POST {{baseUrl}}/hipporag/qa
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "queries": [
    "What connects neural networks to computer vision applications through convolutional layers?"
  ],
  "dataset_id": "default",
  "num_to_retrieve": 10,
  "generate_answer": true
}

### Standard Hybrid Search (for direct matches)
POST {{baseUrl}}/search/hybrid
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "query": "neural networks computer vision convolutional layers",
  "top_k": 10,
  "vector_weight": 0.7,
  "text_weight": 0.3
}

